snippet.title: Stones of the Revenant - Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
Stones of the Revenant is coming to Nintendo Switch early 2020! 

Choose from 6 playable characters. Team up with your friends to destroy the Stones and defeat the Revenant! 

Stones of the Revenant is an arcade style action platformer with two-player local co-op.
